-/
variables {ùïú : Type*} [field ùïú] [topological_space ùïú] [topological_ring ùïú]

/--
The map `Œª x, a * x + b`, as a homeomorphism from `ùïú` (a topological field) to itself, when `a ‚â† 0`.
-/
